00:30:56,875 --> 00:30:59,083
My devotee is going to encounter
significant trouble.

620
00:30:59,291 --> 00:31:03,416
Take someone from my Shivgan
who can help him.

621
00:31:03,541 --> 00:31:04,708
As You wish, Lord.

622
00:31:29,125 --> 00:31:34,000
