Remember that.

761
00:38:14,833 --> 00:38:18,833
I wonder why this city of knowledge
is filled with ignorant people, son.

762
00:38:19,083 --> 00:38:20,041
Mister...

763
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,708
